{"tid":669633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬警方：前總理納吉布住家搜出七十二箱現金、珠寶","createTime":"2018-05-18T15:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T15:32:37.000Z","uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2100816021e896ba253edf63b171e3fbd2df004","tid":669633,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2429907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2429907&d=8HhhJffOGWxBLVTaJGqiTwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=afbc78bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2429907&h=ba0748b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2429907</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php17iKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php17iKpu.jpg&h=5c9a69a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞前總理納吉布（Najib Razak）住處搜出的現金、珠寶、奢侈品，裝滿了72個行李箱。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕馬來西亞前總理納吉布（Najib Razak）涉嫌貪污45億美元（約新台幣1338億元），住家於16日遭到搜索，大馬警方今（18日）透露，納吉布住處搜出的現金、珠寶、奢侈品，足足裝滿了72個行李箱。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，馬來西亞新任總理馬哈地（Mahathir Mohamad）於17日召開記者會表示，警方有足夠的理由搜索納吉布的住所，並強調所有犯罪案件已在調查中，無論涉案者是誰，政府都會展開行動。<br />\n<br />\n警方除了在納吉布豪宅發現裝滿72個行李箱的大量珠寶、各式貨幣現金之外，還有將近300個知名設計師手提包，包括LV與愛馬仕等奢華品牌。由於數量龐大，還未估計出這些物品的總值。此外，針對納吉布其他房產的搜索，也發現了疑似與貪汙案有關的文件，目前納吉布與妻子已被境管避免潛逃。"},{"pid":"5f624ee07e93a7daab81b180e9cc6d5ec02257fd","tid":669633,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"大清洗"},{"pid":"d3e3acd68e4d6fcdd6d7b1c9718c0d4757674ba9","tid":669633,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}